{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Humanity has been exiled from Earth by ruthless alien invaders. We now cling to survival in derelict stations and outposts scattered throughout the solar system. As the last hope for mankind, you must navigate the remnants of civilization, uncover lost technologies, and fight for humanity\u2019s future.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Vortica is a twin-stick shooter roguelite where you take on a variety of missions across the solar system. As one of humanity\u2019s last survivors, you will brave hostile territories, rescue stranded civilians, and track down deadly alien threats, all while scavenging for the resources needed to stay alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3538260/extras/SpiderCrawl.gif?t=1739918042\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">BATTLE ALIEN HORDES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage in heart-pounding battles against massive alien hordes, decimating foes by the hundreds with your arsenal of weapons. Amidst the chaos, strategically deploy automated turrets to bolster your defenses and turn the tide of battle in your favor. Each encounter becomes a test of skill and strategy as you adapt to the ever-changing battlefield. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3538260/extras/SwarmGif2.gif?t=1739918042\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">EXPLORE DYNAMIC WORLDS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Using advanced procedural generation, every level presents a unique and coherent layout, ensuring that no two missions are ever alike. Whether you're navigating dark winding corridors or traversing the harsh surface of Venus, each environment poses its own set of challenges and opportunities. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CUSTOMIZE YOUR GEAR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 100 items at your disposal, each offering distinct abilities and mechanics. With so many different equipment options and potential synergies, the possibilities for customizing your loadout are endless, allowing for unique playstyles and tactics to emerge with each combination. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3538260/extras/ItemGif.gif?t=1739918042\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CHALLENGE EPIC BOSSES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Prepare to face off against terrifying bosses that will test your skills to their limits. These colossal adversaries stand as the ultimate challenge in your quest to reclaim Earth. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3538260/extras/BossGif.gif?t=1739918042\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3538260?t=1739918042","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3538260/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739918042","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3538260/82c18a7ea923169bd2ea45aae3382715d81d0a26/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739918042","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3538260/82c18a7ea923169bd2ea45aae3382715d81d0a26/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739918042","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Humanity has been exiled from Earth by ruthless alien invaders. We now cling to survival in derelict stations and outposts scattered throughout the solar system. As t